title: A Closer Look At The Housing Market
itunes:title: A Closer Look At The Housing Market
description:
Brad Dillman, Chief Economist for Cortland, talks housing data. Ataman Ozyildirim, Director of Economic Research and Global Research Chair at the Conference Board, on the monthly LEI data. Robert Lam, Co-Head of Credit at Man Numeric, discusses strategies driving ESG integration into fixed income markets. Chris Gaffney, President of World Markets at TIAA Bank, talks markets and the Fed. Hosted by Paul Sweeney and Matt Miller.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
